~ unhinged_girl_enter

do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat_enter")
do wait(GlobalManager.current_animation_length)
do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat_idle")
do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl_enter")
do wait(GlobalManager.current_animation_length)
do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl_idle")
Girl: Oh hey. I heard about you.

Girl: I have a job for you
Girl: There are some... undesirables making fun of me.
Girl: And now they are just sailing and falling in love.
Girl: Here, have this. (Bowling ball appears in the inventory)
Girl: Smoke these fools

do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl_leave")
do wait(GlobalManager.current_animation_length)

=> END!

~ boat_enter

if GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "bowling_ball"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat", "hit")

	People on a boat: !
	People on a boat: (boat sinks)
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat_leave")
	do wait(GlobalManager.current_animation_length)
	=> capitalist_first_enter

elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "heart"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat", "hit")

	automat: are you evil?
	People on a boat: Are we evil hun?
	People on a boat: No, I don't think so.
	=> END!
	
elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "mind"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat", "hit")

	automat: Why are you bullying her?
	People on a boat: We are not bullying anybody. 
	People on a boat: That's my sister who wanted to come along, but we really needed some alone time
	=> END!
	
elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "guts"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat", "hit")

	automat: Cease your evildoing right now!
	People on a boat: O-Okay!
	=> END!
else
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("boat", "hit")
	Sorry I cannot really here you from here
	=> END!
(if the player talks to the boat 2 times and does not shoot the bowling ball, the girl appears again)

~ unhinged_girl_enter2
elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "safety donut"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl", "hit")
	automat: Here!
	Girl: I don't see how this is a weapon

	=> END!
	
elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "fish food"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl", "hit")
	automat: Catch!
	Girl: You cant open the lid
	Girl: I am going to perish
	=> END!

elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "bowling ball"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl", "hit")
	automat: Have it back!
	Girl: At them partner, not me!
	=> END!
	
elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "heart"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl", "hit")

	automat: I don't know if this is a good idea
	Girl: What do you mean?
	Girl: This should sink them well
	Girl: I don't think finding anything heavier would help
	=> END!
	
elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "mind"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl", "hit")

	automat: Is this really necessary? Why not talk to them?
	Girl: They don't want to talk to me!
	=> END!
	
elif GlobalManager.item_that_hit.item_name == "guts"
	do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("unhinged_girl", "hit")
	automat: But I don't think we should shoot them
	Um well...
	But I want them to spend time with me!

______________________________________
I get it! I guess we WON'T sink them, happy?
I will just drown instead, because nobody likes me.


