~ capitalist_first_enter

do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("capitalist_enter")
do wait(GlobalManager.current_animation_length)
do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("capitalist_idle")

capitalist: Tak a konec dema
capitalist: Škoda
capitalist: Vypni hru

capitalist: Aaah přemáhá mě pokračování mého scénáře

 - How do I make money? =>< know_me_disagree
	do wait(0)
	~ know_me_disagree
	do wait(0)
	capitalist: Real funny
	=> capitalist_end_convo

 - But what even is money? =>< know_me_agree
	do wait(0)
	~ know_me_agree
	capitalist: I care way too little about you to explain
	capitalist: Please try to exist usefully
	=> capitalist_end_convo


~ capitalist_end_convo
capitalist: I am off to pouring water out of my sunken house
capitalist: I will be back

do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("capitalist_leave")
do wait(GlobalManager.current_animation_length)
=> duckman

